message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with audio tagging, which is a subfield of sound processing. cs.CV is the second most likely category as the paper uses pretrained state-of-the-art image recognition networks for the video branch. cs.CL is the third most likely category as the paper mentions that the proposed framework can be easily carried over to other audio tasks such as speech sentimental analysis. cs.LG is the fourth most likely category as the paper uses convolutional and recurrent neural networks for the audio branch. cs.MM is the fifth most likely category as the paper deals with multimodal learning.
